      <p>Dr. Joshbert Zands is the founding professor of Crypto-zoonotic-micro-mycology at UC Borehamwood. He discovered <em>Porphyromyces indignatus</em>, the ideological fungus now feared and misunderstood across academic and political circles alike.</p>
