      <h2>Press & Media</h2>
      <p><strong>Spore Signals:</strong> "Tell us about your childhood."<br><strong>Zands:</strong> Unlike my father, whose greatest scientific contribution was avoiding taxes, I studied fungi to escape his conservatory-based worldview.</p>
